{"tid":277491,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)奪命西 致命ID","createTime":"2017-06-09T15:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T19:07:01.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81c8aa1fec4dda55fd9ccf9d482bc79fa8271ba3","tid":277491,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=BpN9fCDnh%2FVsk4kBd7LYQIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e87a1fa8\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=BpN9fCDnh%2FVsk4kBd7LYQIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9f5fb3c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=BpN9fCDnh%2FVsk4kBd7LYQIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f264a85f\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/22/A_Million_Ways_to_Die_in_the_West_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F22%2FA_Million_Ways_to_Die_in_the_West_poster.jpg&h=6c098468&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3d/Identity_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3d%2FIdentity_movie.jpg&h=fa7f9429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1880年代的亞利桑那州，懦弱的牧羊人阿爾伯特性感火辣的女朋友路易絲被搶走，而他的情敵是一個無惡不做、槍法一流的大壞蛋福伊。阿爾伯特面臨的最大難題是如何打敗情敵挽回女友芳心。此時一位神秘女子安娜來到鎮上幫助他練習槍法，為他找回了奪回女友的信心。可是在相處中，阿爾伯特卻慢慢愛上了安娜。緊接著安娜的惡棍丈夫克林奇也跟隨而至，阿爾伯特的麻煩似乎越來越大....<br />\n<br />\n2.連夜的暴雨，把曾擔任警官的司機艾德（約翰&middot;庫薩克飾）等十個陌生人困在一間沙漠中的汽車旅館內，他們原本只是想等待雨過天青之後，繼續自己的旅程與工作。誰知隨即發生一連串的謀殺案，讓他們互相猜忌，每個人都想要逃出生天，所以互相警戒、防備，深畏無法逃離人魔的掌心。但是後來他們發現，十個人的生日竟然是同一天&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947ad1faeee40514be531c8ff4aa833533e909df","tid":277491,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3666bcf33bb94d1fd85331ce3dbbd94ff61b5fb9","tid":277491,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a30b5b7a592d261c3089ef001e82cd1b3b0c6f","tid":277491,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0c3e53162114c76b5e866ce3b8518f965e3f11","tid":277491,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad77e9000c2e403d94670f979d6830b839ac29c","tid":277491,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" clas